name: Another/BIRTHDAY [4°] ~ New Cycle
description:
____----____----____----____----___

"On October 4, 1992, in the city of Santarém, Pará, Amazon, Brazil, a person was born who would be called Marcos Daniel.  Yes!  It is me.  Today is my birthday, and I'm releasing this piece to celebrate this date that for me is so important.  A ''New Cycle" starts and with it new possibilities. Symbolically I decided to make 29 editions (my age) and sell (swap) 28 for the price of 0,4XTZ. So, if you want to support me and make my day very happy, collect it 👽
